Intesa to Buy Stake in Carpisa, Yamamay Holding, Corriere Says

-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-12-12T07:25:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-12/intesa-to-buy-stake-in-carpisa-yamamay-holding-corriere-says.html
Intesa Sanpaolo SpA (ISP)  may buy a 10
percent stake in Pianoforte Holding, which controls the Yamamy
and Carpisa retail stores,  Corriere della Sera  reported, citing
the chairman of the holding.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonia Sirletti in Milan at 
 ssirletti@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  